            "answer_text": "That rather depends where you stand in the United States? You have a choice of\u2026 Canada (Oh yes! Going south from Detroit can get you into Canada!)Antarctica (not really a country - but still!) South of Hawaii & Alaska.Honduras - South of AlabamaCuba - South of FloridaColombia - South of Guantanamo Bay!!Bahamas - South of the CarolinasTurks & Caicos - South of Rhode IslandHaiti - South of Long IslandDominican Republic - South of Cape CodThe Netherlands - South of Maine!!![math]^a[/math]Venezuela - South of MaineOh - and\u2026 Mexico - South of quite a lot of places! [math]\\quad\\quad\\quad\\quad\\quad\\quad\\quad\\quad[/math] USA and its \u2018Southern Shadow\u2019   [math]^a[/math] The island of Bonaire is part of the Netherlands. [Thanks to Scollay Petry for putting me on the track of this little place] ",
